---
title: Easy Moroccan Beef & Pork Meatball Tagine with Rapid Rice & Greek Yoghurt
description: Baking beef and pork meatballs in the oven with the warm mild spices and then baking them again in a rich chermoula sauce will
help all those flavours to soak in. When you dig in be sure to savour the taste, it’s well worth the wait.
